name: Voyager Official Committee of Unsecured Creditors

tweet: 1/ The UCC's goal has and continues to be returning assets to creditors as quickly as possible. The process for doing so is not simple and must be done within the confines of the Bankruptcy Code.
name: Voyager Official Committee of Unsecured Creditors

tweet: We want to make clear that the FTX/Voyager transaction has not been consummated. Voyager has not transferred any crypto or other assets to FTX in connection with the transaction. The UCC will take all steps necessary to protect creditors’ interest. We are evaluating all options.
name: Voyager Official Committee of Unsecured Creditors

tweet: We are actively evaluating all of the news regarding FTX and how it may impact the Voyager transaction. We will provide additional information to the community as soon as possible.
name: Voyager Official Committee of Unsecured Creditors

tweet: The UCC has an obligation to maximize value for all creditors regardless of the type or amount of their claims. All creditor interests are being taken into account for every decision made by the UCC.

tweet: There is a lot of information floating around in the media about the auction. Do not assume that what you read is true. Those involved in the auction are bound by confidentiality, and no one is authorized to disclose anything that has occurred.
name: Voyager Official Committee of Unsecured Creditors

tweet: We know everyone is eager to hear results from the auction, but its not over and we have just adjourned for the evening. We will continue as long as it takes to reach the highest and best bid.
